description: President Trump says construction for the wall is underway. We mapped the current fencing and what his administration has done so far.
title: Trump Wants a Border Wall. See What’s in Place Already.
title_page: Trump Wants a Border Wall. See What’s in Place Already. - The New York Times
maintext: The government has built nearly 700 miles of wall and fencing since 2006, mostly on federal land and where the terrain does not provide a natural barrier.
